[SN]TITLE[SN]
Vintage 'steam bus' tours Weston-super-Mare's seafront

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A vintage steam-powered bus, which has been recently restored, is the latest tourist attraction on the seafront at Weston-super-Mare.

